{
  "name": "USER_INFO-page",
  "elements": [

    {
      "type": "panel",
      "name": "UserInfoPanel",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "html",
          "name": "UserInfoLifeStatusHeading",
          "html": "<h2>Before We Begin</h2>"
        },
        {
        "type": "html",
          "name": "UserInfoLifeStatusText",
          "html": "<p>We know how hard it is to lose one's beloved companion animal. If you're still grieving from the loss, maybe it's best to do the survey later when you've had time to heal. </p><p>If you'd like to continue now, now please tell us your LP companion's name and if they have crossed over the Rainbow Bridge. This will help us avoid questions that are inappropriate for your situation.</p>"
        },
        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "UserInfoLifeStatusDetailsPanel",
          "elements": [
            {
            "type": "text",
            "name": "CmpnName",
            "title": "Please tell us your companion's name:",
            "isRequired": true
            },
            {
              "type": "imagepicker",
              "name": "LifeStatus",
              "title": "Has {CmpnName} crossed over the Rainbow Bridge?",
              "isRequired": true,
              "visibleIf": "{CmpnName} notempty",
              "choices": [
              {
                  "value": true,
                  "imageLink": "./img-companions-rainbow.png",
                  "text": "Over the Rainbow Bridge"
                },
                {
                  "value": false,
                  "imageLink": "./img-companions.png",
                  "text": "Still here on Earth"
                }

              ],
              "imageWidth": 120,
              "imageHeight": 120,
              "showLabel": true
            }

          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "html",
          "name": "UserInfoHeading",
          "html": "<h2>About You</h2>"
        },
        {
          "type": "html",
          "name": "UserInfoText",
          "html": "<p>We're asking for your first name, which country you live in, and some optional demographics to help us understand the people who are making choices for their beloved LP companions. We also ask for contact info to prevent fake respondents and make sure each respondent is unique and verifiable.</p>"
        },
        {
          "type": "html",
          "name": "UserInfoVerificationHeading",
          "html": "<h3>Verification Contact</h3>"
        },
        {
          "type": "html",
          "name": "UserInfoVerificationPanelText",
          "html": "<p>We contact a random sample of respondents for verification purposes. You may or may not be contacted. You can provide an email address or, if you're more comfortable communicating via Facebook Messenger, you can provide your Facebook account name.</p><p>With your consent, we may also contact you to talk in more detail about your experience with LP.</p>"
        },
        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "UserInfoVerificationPanel", 
          "elements": [

            {
              "type": "boolean",
              "name": "UserInfoContactType",
              "title": "Would you like to use email or Facebook Messenger for verification?",
              "isRequired": true,
              "labelTrue": "Facebook",
              "labelFalse": "Email"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "title": "Email address:",
              "name": "UserInfoContactTypeEmail",
              "isRequired": true,
              "visibleIf": "{UserInfoContactType} = false",
              "inputType": "email"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "UserInfoContactTypeFacebookInstructions",
              "title": "z",
              "visibleIf":"{UserInfoContactType} = true",
              "html": "<div class='srvy-general-info'><img src='/img-info-icon.png' class='srvy-info-icon' alt='Example image' />&nbsp;Please go to your Facebook account page and copy the URL, then paste it below. Example: https://facebook.com/my.user.name.</div>"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "title": "Facebook account:",
              "name": "UserInfoContactTypeFacebook",
              "isRequired": true,
              "visibleIf": "{UserInfoContactType} = true",
              "placeholder": "eg. https://www.facebook.com/my.profile.name",
              "validators": [
                {
                  "type": "regex",
                  "regex": "^(https?:\\/\\/)?(www\\.)?facebook\\.com\\/[a-zA-Z0-9.]{5,}$",
                  "text": "Please enter a valid Facebook profile URL, e.g., https://facebook.com/your.username"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "boolean",
              "name": "UserInfoContactOK",
              "title": "May we contact you to talk more about your LP experience?",
              "isRequired": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "html",
          "name": "UserInfoNameCountryHeading",
          "html": "<h3>Your First Name and Country</h3>"
        },
        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "UserInfoAboutPanel", 
          "elements": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "title": "First Name:",
              "name": "UserInfoFirstName",
              "isRequired": true
            },
            {
              "type": "dropdown",
              "name": "UserInfoCountry",
              "title": "Country:",
              "isRequired": true,
              "choices": [
                { "value": "US",
                  "text": "United States"
                },
                { "value": "UK",
                  "text": "United Kingdom"
                },
                { "value": "CA",
                  "text": "Canada"
                },
                { "value": "DE",
                  "text": "Germany"
                },
                { "value": "AU/NZ",
                  "text": "Australia/New Zealand"
                },
                { "value": "FR",
                  "text": "France"
                },
                { "value": "ES",
                  "text": "Spain"
                },
                { "value": "PT",
                  "text": "Portugal"
                }
              ],
              "showOtherItem": true
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "name": "UserInfoStateRegion",
              "title": "What state, province or region do you live in (optional)",
              "isRequired": false
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "html",
          "name": "UserInfoAgeGenderHeading",
          "html": "<h3>Age and Gender (optional)</h3>"
        },
        {
          "type": "html",
          "name": "UserInfoAgeGenderText",
          "html": "<p>We're asking for basic demographic information to help understand how different people manage the animals in their care.</p>"
        },
        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "UserInfoAgeGenderPanel",
          "elements": [
            {
              "type": "dropdown",
              "name": "UserInfoAgeGroup",
              "title": "Approximately what is your age?",
               "width": "70%",
              "minWidth": "260px",
              "choices": [
                {
                  "value": "UNDER_20",
                  "text": "Under 20"
                },
                {
                  "value": "20_34",
                  "text": "20-34"
                },
                {
                  "value": "35_49",
                  "text": "35-49"
                },
                "50-64",
                {
                  "value": "OVER_65",
                  "text": "Over 65"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "radiogroup",
              "name": "UserInfoGender",
              "title": "Gender information:",
              "isRequired": false,
              "colCount": 3,
              "choices": [
                {
                "value": "WOMAN",
                "text": "Woman"
                },
                {
                  "value": "MAN",
                  "text": "Man"
                },
                {
                  "value": "NON_BINARY",
                  "text": "Non-binary"
                },
                {
                  "value": "NOT_SAY",
                  "text": "Prefer not to say"
                }
              ],
              "showOtherItem": true,
              "otherText": "Prefer to self-describe"
            }
          ]
        }

      ]
    }
  ]
}